    title: "Direct Brand vs Broker Deals: Which Saves You More Money?",
    metaTitle: "Direct vs Broker Vacation Deals: Which Saves More?",
    metaDescription: "Should you book vacation deals directly with the resort or through a broker? We compare pricing, flexibility, and risks to help you save the most money in 2026.",
    category: "brands",
    publishDate: "2026-03-14",
    author: "Editorial Team",
    readTime: "10 min read",
