    slug: "how-vacation-deal-brokers-work",
    title: "How Vacation Deal Brokers Work (And How to Get the Best Price)",
    metaTitle: "How Vacation Deal Brokers Work: Insider Guide",
    metaDescription: "How vacation deal brokers like BookVIP and GetawayDealz actually work behind the scenes. The business model, pricing secrets, and how to negotiate the best deal.",
    category: "brands",
